The [[Project:KDE|Gentoo KDE team]] maintains the [https://gitweb.gentoo.org/proj/kde.git/ kde overlay]. This [[overlay]] contains live ebuilds, upstream pre-releases, works-in-progress, and other things not yet ready or otherwise unsuitable for the main tree.

== Using the overlay ==

The easiest way to enable the KDE overlay is with [[layman]]:
{{RootCmd|layman --fetch --add kde}}

